title: ‘Heap big lies!’ Elizabeth Warren twists and turns to prove claim about Sessions, knots herself up
text:
Notice how Warren wasn’t overly concerned about AG Lynch hanging out with Bubba on a private plane right before the election. RUSSIA! @charlescwcooke @chadfelixg heap big lies from @SenWarren sendum' up false smoke signals 
— Sweater Yams (@Sweater_Yams_) March 2, 2017 
LOL. 
— mbc (@MoonbatCatnip) March 2, 2017 
All jump and nonsense … in fact that could be a campaign slogan for Warren and many of her Democratic cohorts. @charlescwcooke Warren isn't dumb, thinks her followers are. I bet Sessions reheard Leahy's Q when Franken verbally asked a broader Q. 
— Tom Maguire (@Tom_Maguire) March 2, 2017 
Knows her followers are dumb – FIFY. @charlescwcooke EW thinks she has a "Gotcha." I truly don't think she gets this whole connecting dots thing. Might have my 5 y/o explain 
— Michael J. Arney (@GrumpyMike88) March 2, 2017 
She really does seen to think this is a gotcha moment, even though she steps in it with her own tweets. The question was in regard to the election, even Warren herself says so. @charlescwcooke As a MA resident I have a Q for @SenWarren ? What meaningful legislation have you authored for us? @HowieCarrShow
